            <div className="showcase-item top-right">
              <div style={{position:'relative',zIndex:1}}>
                <div className="showcase-tag-gold" style={{marginBottom:16}}>First in India</div>
                <div style={{marginBottom:16}}>
                  <svg style={{width:36,height:36,color:'rgba(201,168,76,.5)'}} fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={1.5} d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 style={{fontFamily:'Fraunces,serif',fontSize:'clamp(20px,2.5vw,26px)',fontWeight:700,color:'#F5F0E8',marginBottom:12}}>EquityShield</h3>
                <p style={{fontSize:13,lineHeight:1.7,color:'rgba(245,240,232,.5)'}}>Banks sell distressed properties at auction for a fraction of their value. We step in before that happens and sell at full market rate — so you don&apos;t lose everything when things go wrong.</p>
